{"tid":246372,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"老娘的草根飯堂 - 蝦膠釀雞翼","createTime":"2017-05-17T03:05:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-20T16:40:20.000Z","uid":30742,"like":80,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"eee1966f919eeb8effa8b3cff82ac29c86f6405b","tid":246372,"uid":30742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T03:05:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/Ni1zj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FNi1zj.jpg&h=e5490903&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/V2TB0A5ao7A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FV2TB0A5ao7A&d=qOmKSCuv03M2cFfeadZVWk%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=0ace8cbb\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/V2TB0A5ao7A</a><br />\n<br />\n朋友想我拍雞翼拆骨片，拖了好耐終於剪輯好了！(對唔住呀攪咁耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ！！)<br />\n本身想釀芝士玉米的，但去街市見到d蝦就好似釀蝦膠仲好吃！<br />\n就變成了蝦膠釀雞翼<br />\n呢個係焗爐版的，其實可以煎，一樣好食！<br />\n<br />\n呢個拆骨方法同我平時拆雞中翼差唔多！<br />\n下次可以試試連雞鎚一齊拆！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n蝦膠釀雞翼 圖文食譜:&nbsp;<br />\n<a href=\"http://oldlady0914.blogspot.hk/2017/05/stuffed-chicken-wings-with-minced-shrimp.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Foldlady0914.blogspot.hk%2F2017%2F05%2Fstuffed-chicken-wings-with-minced-shrimp.html&d=qOmKSCuv03M2cFfeadZVWk%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=df2f1608\" target=\"_blank\">http://oldlady0914.blogspot.hk/2017/05/stuffed-chicken-wings-with-minced-shrimp.html</a><br />\nFacebook :&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/oldladycanteen/&nbsp;\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Foldladycanteen%2F%C2%A0&d=qOmKSCuv03M2cFfeadZVWk%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=ae088121\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/oldladycanteen/&nbsp;</a><br />\nInstagram:&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/_oldlady_/&nbsp;\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2